<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>It's a match with {{matchName}}!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background: #fafaf9;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .logo-text {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: #a07855;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
    }
    .celebration {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 48px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #525252;
    }
    .intro-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin: 28px 0;
      border: 2px solid #a07855;
    }
    .match-name {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .match-email {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #a07855;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .match-email a {
      color: #a07855;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .match-email a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .shared-interest {
      background: #fef3c7;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #78350f;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .context {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #525252;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .conversation-starters {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 24px 0;
    }
    .conversation-starters h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #166534;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .conversation-starters ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #14532d;
    }
    .conversation-starters li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .cta {
      background: #a07855;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .cta p {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .cta strong {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e4;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #737373;
    }
    .success-note {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
      padding: 16px 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #14532d;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-text">grove</div>
    </div>

    <div class="celebration">✨</div>

    <h1>It's a mutual match!</h1>

    <p>Excellent news, {{userName}}!</p>

    <p>You and <strong>{{matchName}}</strong> both expressed interest in connecting. We're excited to introduce you!</p>

    <div class="intro-card">
      <div class="match-name">{{matchName}}</div>
      <div class="match-email">
        <a href="mailto:{{matchEmail}}">{{matchEmail}}</a>
      </div>

      <div class="shared-interest">
        <strong>What you have in common:</strong> {{sharedInterest}}
      </div>

      <div class="context">
        {{context}}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="conversation-starters">
      <h3>Conversation starters:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Share what specifically drew you to connect</li>
        <li>Ask about their current project or area of exploration</li>
        <li>Suggest a coffee chat or async exchange to start</li>
        <li>Be genuine about what you're looking for in this connection</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="cta">
      <p><strong>Ready to connect?</strong></p>
      <p>We recommend reaching out within the next few days while the momentum is fresh!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="success-note">
      We love seeing meaningful connections happen. After you've had a chance to connect,
      we'd appreciate hearing how it went. We'll follow up in a week to ask for quick feedback.
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: #525252; margin-top: 30px;">
      <strong>Tips for a great first conversation:</strong><br>
      • Be curious and open-minded<br>
      • Share your authentic interests and goals<br>
      • Respect their time and communication preferences<br>
      • Follow up if it feels like a good fit!
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        <strong>Grove</strong> – Professional connection matching<br>
        This email was sent to {{recipientEmail}}
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #a3a3a3;">
        This introduction was made because you both indicated mutual interest.
        Happy connecting!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
